# 🎬 Movie Extension — Full Code Review

## Project Overview

| Attribute | Detail |
|---|---|
| **Type** | Chrome Extension (Manifest V3) |
| **Purpose** | Detect movies on Hotstar/Prime Video, track watch history, show personalized recommendations via TMDb API |
| **Total Source Files** | 11 JS/HTML/CSS files |
| **External Dependencies** | Zero (vanilla JS) |
| **API** | TMDb (The Movie Database) |

